==Tips==
[[File:Brine rat safespot.png|thumb|Location of the brine rat safespot.<br/>(South-east corner)]]
*There are two safespots, one being the black bones to the south-east, and the other in the north-west corner of the cave. If the brine rats are in the top half of the cave, you are able to safespot them from behind the bones in the corner.
*Brine rats frequently drop [[raw swordfish]] and occasionally drop unnoted [[raw shark]]s in addition to [[raw rat meat]], so bringing a [[tinderbox]] and a couple of [[logs]] may be advisable. Alternatively, [[Olaf]], outside the caverns, has a permanent [[fire]] located beside him, so players can collect the unnoted raw fish/rat meat drops and cook them on his fire if they are willing to exit and re-enter the caverns multiple times.

